    "The app, called Near, has one sole purpose: Look for smart glasses nearby and warn you.\n\nThis app notifies you when smart glasses are nearby. It uses company identifiers in the Bluetooth data sent out by these. Therefore, there likely are false positives (e.g. from VR headsets). Hence, please proceed with caution when approaching a person nearby wearing glasses. They might just be regular glasses, despite this app’s warning.\n\nThe app’s author Henriques Pontes takes no liability whatsoever for this app nor it’s functionality. Use at your own risk. By technical design, detecting Bluetooth LE devices might sometimes just not work as expected." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the app's purpose.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "The device is in the immediate vicinity (same room or table)." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Das Gerät befindet sich in der unmittelbaren Umgebung (gleicher Raum oder Tisch)."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "El dispositivo está en las inmediaciones (misma habitación o mesa)."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "L'appareil est dans l'environnement immédiat (même pièce ou table)."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Il dispositivo si trova nelle immediate vicinanze (stessa stanza o tavolo)."
          }
        },
        "pt" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "O dispositivo está na vizinhança imediata (mesma sala ou mesa)."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "设备就在附近（同一个房间 or 桌子）。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The Near app continuously parses Bluetooth Low Energy advertisements. Ray-Ban Meta glasses emit periodic BLE pulses to negotiate data transfers, letting us detect them even if recording is not actively running." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Die Near-App analysiert kontinuierlich Bluetooth Low Energy-Signale. Ray-Ban Meta-Brillen senden regelmäßige BLE-Impulse zur Datenübertragung aus, sodass wir sie auch dann erkennen können, wenn keine aktive Aufnahme läuft."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "La aplicación Near analiza continuamente los anuncios de Bluetooth Low Energy. Las gafas Ray-Ban Meta emiten pulsos BLE periódicos para negociar transferencias de dados, lo que permite detectarlas incluso si la grabación no está activa."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "L'application Near analyse en continu les signaux Bluetooth Low Energy. Les lunettes Ray-Ban Meta émettent des impulsos BLE périodiques pour négocier les transferts, ce qui permet de les détecter même si l'enregistrement n'est pas actif."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "L'app Near analizza continuamente i pacchetti Bluetooth Low Energy. Gli occhiali Ray-Ban Meta emettono impulsi BLE periodici per negoziare i trasferimenti di dati, permettendoci di rilevarli anche se la registrazione non è attiva."
          }
        },
        "pt" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "O app Near analisa continuamente os anúncios do Bluetooth Low Energy. Os óculos Ray-Ban Meta emitem pulsos BLE periódicos para negociar transferências de dados, permitindo a detecção mesmo que a gravação não esteja ativa."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Near 应用持续解析蓝牙低功耗 (BLE) 广播。Ray-Ban Meta 眼镜会定期发送 BLE 脉冲以协商数据传输，因此即使录制未激活，我们也能检测到它们。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The smart glasses are likely on a person right next to you." : {
